======Sets auto kick player.======
= Description =

Controls who can join the server. Player doesn't have enough experience or promotion, player will be auto kicked by server. 

See also [[asw_autokick_player_experience.wiki|asw_autokick_player_experience]] and [[asw_autokick_player_promotion.wiki|asw_autokick_player_promotion]] to work
